 on transient signals. We also present a script\nwhich uses the differences between the two strategies, and known differences\nbetween transient RFI and astrophysical transients, to notify the observer when\na potential transient is in the data stream.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Apr 2018 19:52:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-16"}
