he\nMLRK validation, the combination of numerical model fields and observed\nclimatologies has been investigated and the results show that this integrated\napproach provides more accurate high-resolution climatologies over the Country.\nThe numerical background introduces valuable information over remote and\nmountainous regions, whereas in-situ data correct for model biases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Apr 2018 10:01:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-16"}
