uture work by utilising\nsynthetic observations from numerical simulations of HII regions. We also\noutline how this shape analysis has further applications to other diffuse\nastronomical objects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Apr 2018 13:41:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-02"}
